snippet.title: Beat Your Meat Early Access Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Are you ready to Beat Your Meat? You and up to 3 friends and battle it out to become boss hog! 

Coming to Steam Early Access in 31st May 2019!

Check it out over on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1013290/Beat_Your_Meat/

Or Join the Discord:
https://discord.gg/bprYfVj
